commit.message: Converted creating walks to be dynamic so it links up to Parse to pull dogs. It also properly creates PlayDates and links it back to the user. Walking map now shows marker of where you are headed. Added extra page solely to view other person's profile.
Dynamically display your list of dogs. These are populated in a grid and will display data accurate from Parse. Removed unnecessary screens. Added in Facebook login to log into Parse.
Added PlayDate class and allowed creating them and sending to Parse.
Added Parse in place of AWS which was having issues. Added Dog model class. Allowed Dogs to be created and pushed to Parse.
Removed extra screens and data that were marked as non-mvp. Switched some screens around.
Completed visuals for page to add dog.
non functional button and camera code added.
Added a temporary login screen. Added a screen to generate new walks and add new dogs. Updated profile to show dogs.
changed async lambda caller to include self in params
